The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation
		 Sunday, January 25, 2004 				 Rap on Ameeta
																								Lucknow, Jan. 24 (PTI): The BJP today issued a show cause notice to Ameeta Singh, a former minister and party MLA from Amethi, asking her to explain her reported statement that she was ready to join the Congress.																								Ameeta, wife of Sanjay Singh, the scion of Amethi, had met Priyanka Gandhi Vadra and Rahul Gandhi during their recent visit there.																								BJP state legislature party leader Lalji Tandon, in the notice, asked Ameeta to explain her stand on the issue, party sources said.																								Ameeta had reportedly said that she was awaiting a nod from the AICC president to join the Congress.
